s/2025/02/red-hot-chili-peppers@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/red-hot-chili-peppers@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/red-hot-chili-peppers@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">，Red Hot Chili Peppers</a>希望以3.5亿美元的价格出售其录制的音乐目录 - 在下面了解更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/red-hot-chili-peppers-cover-interview-2022-unlimited-love-3152682">在封面上 - 红色热辣椒：“我们感觉新鲜，就像新乐队一样”</a></strong></li></ul><p>根据<a href="https://www.billboard.com/pro/red-hot-chili-peppers-shopping-music-catalog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>广告牌</em></a>报告，加利福尼亚乐队的录制大师目录已准备出售，乐队正在寻求至少达到3亿美元的交易。 <em>Billboard</em>还估计，该目录目前每年为该乐队带来约2600万美元。</p><p>目前，Red Hot Chili Peppers拥有通过Warner Music发行的所有13张录音室专辑的大师和权利。目前尚不清楚他们是否还拥有通过EMI发行的前四张专辑的大师。</p><p> <em>Billboard</em>还报告说，Red Hot Chili Peppers可能已经与Warner锁定了大师目录的协议，尽管这尚未得到证实。 </p><figure id="attachment_3755902" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3755902" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3755902" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/rhcp-flea@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/rhcp-flea@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/rhcp-flea@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/rhcp-flea@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/rhcp-flea@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/rhcp-flea@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/rhcp-flea@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3755902" class="wp-caption-text">红辣椒的跳蚤。图片来源：Barry Brecheisen/Wireimage</figcaption></figure><p>这笔3.5亿美元的交易应像他们要求的那样获得，这将是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-hot-chili-peppers-to-sell-songwriting-catalogue-in-100million-deal-2932679">Hipgnosis于2021年为其出版权和歌曲创作目录所支付的1.4亿美元</a>的补充。如果新交易通过，它将积累近5亿美元的加利福尼亚放克罗克人。</p><p>红辣椒辣椒很快将成为出售其目录的最新行为，例如<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">Pink Floyd</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">Queen</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kiss">Kiss</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tame-impala">Tame Impala</a> 。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-floyd-sell-back-catalogue-for-400million-3799093">平克·弗洛伊德（Pink Floyd）于10月以4亿美元的价格将其目录卖给了索尼（Sony）</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tame-impalas-kevin-parker-sells-entire-past-and-future-catalogue-to-sony-music-3756736">驯服的Impala的凯文·帕克（Kevin Parker）将所有过去和将来的目录都卖给了索尼，以获取未公开的款项</a>。</p><p>同样， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kiss-catalogue-brand-name-and-ip-acquired-by-pophouse-3613184">KISS将他们的整个目录，品牌名称，相似性和IP卖给了瑞典娱乐公司和音乐投资公司Pophouse，</a>含量未公开。迄今为止，音乐历史上最昂贵的目录属于皇后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/queen-sell-music-catalogue-to-sony-music-for-over-1billion-3767084">他于去年6月以高达127亿美元的价格出售给索尼</a>，这标志着其自然界最大的收购。</p><p> Red Hot Chili Peppers尚未分享他们2025年的计划，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-red-hot-chili-peppers-fireaid-show-hit-packed-medley-3833538">最近在上个月末在洛杉矶举行的Fireeid Beady Concert演出，</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/entertainment-world-reacts-to-heart-wrenching-los-angeles-wildfires-3827340">今年早些时候席卷了几个社区的毁灭性野火</a>之后，为这座城市筹集了资金。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-hot-chili-peppers-reportedly-seeking-350million-for-recorded-music-catalogue-3839647">据报道，红辣椒邮报（Red Hot Chili Peppers）寻求3.5亿美元的录制音乐目录，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
